text: Here's your chance to own 3 storybook cottages just steps from Cap Sante Marina. These impeccable homes have been remodeled from the ground up with many upgrades and amenities. Be charmed at first sight! These homes have options, live in one and rent the others or rent them all. Enjoy the walking trails along the marina and the Cap Sante Forest Land trails, along with the Frisbee Golf Course. Walkability to shopping, dining, the Farmers Market are a breeze. Home 1 has 1512 SF of living space with 2+ BR and 2.5 BA as well as a 420 SF basement for a shop/workspace/storage. Home 2 has 800 SF of living space with 2 BR and 1 BA. Home 3 has 540 SF of living space with 1 BR and 1 BA.

On the market for the first time in many decades, here is an outstanding opportunity for this creekside acreage fixer! Nestled on 16.9 acres and comprised of a 3 bedroom house and three outbuildings, here's your chance to restore this mid century waterfront gem and create your dream estate! The sale includes 3 separate parcels for a total of 16.9 acres alongside Friday Creek. The 3 bedroom house features charming period details and built-ins. All the primary living spaces are on the main floor, including a spacious bedroom with fantastic creek views. The detached 3 car garage is located just steps from the house. Two additional outbuildings offer flexibility for storage or...you decide! Don't miss this rare find!

Spacious 2, 190 sq. ft. Thunderbird area home: 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bath tri-level, nestled on a desirable corner lot. Welcoming covered front porch and a deck, each perfect for relaxing or entertaining. 2-car attached garage, additional space for parking and room for an RV. Mature trees and tasteful landscape enhance your home's curb appeal and privacy. Inside, boasts a cozy fireplace, a primary bedroom with walk-in closet and private bath. Architectural details such as a stunning wood ceiling in the main living area add warmth and character. Home combines function with aesthetic appeal, making it an ideal choice for anyone seeking space, comfort & style.
nearby_schools: Mount Vernon School District, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Kulshan Ridge! A 2004-built 27-home community celebrates NW wildlife above serene, tree-lined wetlands. Watch & listen for eagles, geese, & hawks as squirrels scamper. Outdoor firepit. Inside is a spacious, open-concept living room, dining & kitchen. The main floor offers 1 bed/office & 1/2 bath. Upstairs is the primary bedroom w/walk-in closet & a full bath, 2 add'l beds & a main bath. A total of 4 beds & 2.5 baths. Attached 420sf 2-car garage w/workbench. N. Gas furnace & cook stove plus heat pump comfort. Pre-inspected, fresh interior paint, new lighting, carpet, & interior doors. Bike or walk the lighted Kulshan Trail W to the Skagit River or E to Mt. Baker Park. Within 1 mile is Skagit Hospital, Skagit College & McIntyre Concert Hall.

Fireplace in Family/kitchen area. Updated main bath, deck off family shaded by a lovely fruit tree with seasonal mountain views.

text: Still time to enjoy the holidays here! 4-bedroom 2.5-bathroom + Office + Bonus, A/C cooled home located in Cambridge Commons boasting a spacious layout. Luxury Vinyl Plank(LVP) flooring throughout the main floor. The covered porch welcomes you into the open-concept living space. The great room is perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing. Primary bedroom features a 5-piece en-suite & a walk-in organizer closet. 3 additional bedrooms, full bath & large bonus room provide ample space for everyone. Over-sized, fenced backyard with cozy firepit for enjoying the PNW! 3-car garage provides plenty of space for vehicles/storage. Community includes fenced dog park, neighborhood park, playground, covered picnic area & Frisbee Golf.

Gorgeous single level country home close to town on a flat 1/3 acre lot. Open concept and thoughtful design with premium materials, including a chefs kitchen with custom cabinetry, expansive concrete counters & island, black stainless steel appliance package, subway tile & an under mount sink. Primary bedroom with tile walk-in shower, second bedroom and bath on one end. Two more bedrooms and a guest bath on the opposite end captures this smart layout. Lots of natural light, birch flooring throughout (no carpet), sound-proof interior wall insulation, insulated & heated garage with workshop space and a brand new heat pump with AC! Awesome private back deck for entertaining, sport court and plenty of yard space for a shop & garden. No HOA.

In West Mount Vernon sits this recently updated tri-level home offering the perfect blend of style and functionality. The sunny living room features a cozy fireplace, seamlessly connecting to the adjoining kitchen and dining area, complete with a slider leading to a spacious deck - ideal for entertaining or relaxing. The lower level boasts a versatile recreation room with a bar, second fireplace, and office nook, providing ample space for work and play. The expansive backyard includes a handy storage shed, while the 2-car garage features an additional one-car shop for hobbies or projects. With thoughtful updates throughout, this home is ready to welcome you!

text: [PRICE IMPROVEMENT] Charming updated 3 bedroom in the sought-after Mount Vernon Hill community! This delightful residence features stylish laminate flooring, completely redone crawlspace, a beautifully renovated bathroom, & durable copper roof. Relax by the cozy wood-burning fireplace or take in the serene outdoors on your FULLY FENCED expansive corner lot, complete with mature privacy trees. Primary bedroom on the main level & 2 more bedrooms + den up. The extra-large detached & heated 2-car garage features new electrical with 220 plug & insulation while offering ample storage, perfect for the car enthusiast. Ideally located near schools, shopping, parks, & easy access to I-5 for convenient commuting. A must-see home that exudes character!
